---
title: Quick Ras El Hanout Beef Stew & Rapid Rice with Currants, Roasted Almonds & Yoghurt
description: Dig into an easy plate of Moroccan-inspired delights! From tender diced beef cooked into a richly spiced stew to
quickly-cooked basmati rice and crunchy roasted almonds, this colourful meal also gets a creamy dollop of yoghurt to
bring the whole flavoursome feast together, and in under 30 minutes!
